When a URL cannot be embedded directly by the "Insert Media" dialog, the user can request that the add-on inspects the remote page to find a supported URL. This means any user allowed to use the "Insert Media" dialog can cause your server to access any remote page, which may be undesirable.
You may also choose to support the author directly with a voluntary donation in EUR or in USD.
